# this recipe was created after realisation that one of my favourite steak houses uses MSG in their steak seasoning

ingredients:

15g black peppercorns, lightly toasted, grounded
15g smoked sweet paprika
30g salt (Celtic or sea salt)
15g garlic powder
10g onion powder
5g coriander seed
10g dill seed
2g cayenne pepper
15g MSG
5g I&G seasoning

Chuck it all together, blended, store.
